cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with image captioning, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method involves processing language and vision information together in a single CNN model, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves word embedding, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR).
